{"word":"G4854 - σύμφυτος - sýmphytos - soom'-foo-tos - Planted together","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύμφυτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sýmphytos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom'-foo-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Planted together</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இணைக்கப்பட்ட - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. connate, congenital, innate, implanted by birth or nature"},{"paragraph":"2. grown together, united with, planted together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5453 - φύω - phýō - foo'-o/5453\">G5453</a>; <i>grown</i> along <i>with</i> (<i>connate</i>), that is, (figuratively) closely <i>united</i> to: - planted together.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4776/4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800/4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806/4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832/4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833/4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854/4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855/4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862/4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880/4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891/4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916/4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957/4957\">G4957</a>"}]}